^5Help - Information
~5USAGE: .information

~5Use this command when you wish to enter lots of information that other
~5users can see.

~5Once you start editing, you may stop (at any time) by merely typing a
~5period on a line by itself.  After that, you will be queried for further
~5action (Save, Quit, Display, or Continue, etc.).

~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help view~5, ^5.help examine

